org.ensembl.variation.datamodel
Class LDFeatureContainer

java.lang.Object
  org.ensembl.variation.datamodel.LDFeatureContainer
public class LDFeatureContainer
extends java.lang.Object

A container for LDFeatures (linkage disequilibrium features) that provides various methods for filtering and accessing the the contained data. Instances of this class can be created manually from a List of LDFeatures and are created by LDFeatureAdaptors.

Author:
Craig Melsopp
See Also:
LDFeature, adaptor which can create instances of this class.
